plot: Rocket is going to be in the Great Sky Race! He'll be competing against all kinds of aircrafts, including the Big Jet. The kids are sure Rocket will win, but as he prepares, Rocket gets the hiccups. The team has to surprise Rocket's hiccups away so he can win the race. They try crashing cymbals, sneaking up on him with a scary tiger and bringing him to a geyser. But in the end, it's a little mouse that surprises Rocket's hiccups away. Rocket gets tot he race in time and beats Big Jet.
